title: BRIEF-Biom'up Announces Approval Of Hemoblast Bellows In Australia

BRIEF-Biom'up Announces Approval Of Hemoblast Bellows In Australia

Stock Markets 15 minutes ago (Oct 07, 2019 17:40)

© Reuters. BRIEF-Biom'up Announces Approval Of Hemoblast Bellows In Australia Oct 7 (Reuters) - BIOM UP SA : * DGAP-NEWS: BIOM'UP ANNOUNCES THE APPROVAL OF HEMOBLAST(TM) BELLOWS AND ITS LAPAROSCOPIC APPLICATOR IN AUSTRALIA * REITERATES ITS REVENUE GUIDANCE IN RANGE OF EUR 4.0 TO 4.5 MILLION FOR 2019 AS ANNOUNCED ON MAY 20, 2019 * FIRST MAJOR SHIPMENT TO LIFE HEALTHCARE DISTRIBUTION PLANNED FOR Q4
